---
import Grid from '~/components/blog/Grid.astro';

import { findLatestPosts } from '~/utils/posts';

const count = 4;
const posts = await findLatestPosts({ count });
---

<section class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-6xl lg:py-20">
	<div class="flex flex-col mb-6 lg:justify-between lg:flex-row md:mb-8">
		<h2 class="max-w-lg mb-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl sm:leading-none lg:mb-5 group font-heading">
			<span class="inline-block mb-1 sm:mb-4">Latest articles<br class="hidden md:block" /> in our Blog</span>
		</h2>

		<p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-400 lg:text-sm lg:max-w-md">
			Nostrud consequat ipsum reprehenderit aliqua. Nisi ut et proident ipsum mollit dolor aliquip eu nisi qui deserunt. Labore occaecat proident aliquip mollit enim adipisicing. Eu sint do eu culpa Lorem voluptate nostrud enim enim exercitation ipsum. Aliqua reprehenderit cillum adipisicing occaecat id ullamco. Laborum veniam Lorem Lorem sunt adipisicing non. Nulla incididunt occaecat qui consequat exercitation deserunt proident enim nulla ullamco.
		</p>
	</div>

	<Grid posts={posts} />
</section>
